  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kurashi Clan, Level 4+ <br />You study the strange jutsu techniques of the Kurashi clan and focus on gaining the utmost efficiency out of your \"creatures\" of shadow. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score by +1, to the maximum of 20.</li><li>Select a number of E-Rank jutsu equal to half your proficiency bonus that you do not already know (excluding <em>True Strike</em>). These jutsu are denoted as <em><strong>Shadow Jutsu</strong></em> for you. You may treat <em><strong>Shadow Jutsu</strong></em> as Kurashi Hijutsu, and may, once per round, cast a Shadow Jutsu without any components nor any actions. You may switch any number of these jutsu on a full rest.</li><li>You gain access to a new <em><strong>Kurashi Skill-Based Action</strong></em> known as <em><strong>Mold Shadow</strong></em> (see the end of this clan).</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
